org.apache.flink.graph.generator

接口 GraphGenerator<K,VV,EV>

  • 类型参数:
    K - the key type for edge and vertex identifiers
    VV - the value type for vertices
    EV - the value type for edges
    所有已知实现类:
    AbstractGraphGenerator, CompleteGraph, CycleGraph, EmptyGraph, GridGraph, HypercubeGraph, PathGraph, RMatGraph, SingletonEdgeGraph, StarGraph

    public interface GraphGenerator<K,VV,EV>
    Graph generators shall be - parallelizable, in order to create large datasets - scale-free, generating the same graph regardless of parallelism - thrifty, using as few operators as possible Graph generators should prefer to emit edges sorted by the source label.
